      "intro": "<center><img class=\"img-fluid atto_image_button_middle\" src=\"https://somas.ouk.ac.ke/ouk_logo.png\" alt=\"logo\" width=\"350\"> <br><br>\r\n<h2>FIRST SEMESTER EXAMINATIONS 2024/2025</h2>\r\n<h3>SECOND YEAR EXAMINATIONS FOR BACHELOR OF SCIENCE IN DATA SCIENCE</h3>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>DSC 201: JULY EXAMINATION</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>JULY  23, 2025           TIME: 1:00PM - 3.00PM</h2>\r\n<hr></center>\r\n<h4>INSTRUCTIONS</h4>\r\n<p style=\"color: #037b90; font-weight: bold;\">Read these instructions before starting the examination. These instruction will be available for reference throughout the examination.</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>This exam consists of 29 questions</li>\r\n<li>You should attempt ALL questions. Marks for each question are indicated alongside the question.</li>\r\n<li>All questions will be displayed in the system and the system MUST be used to input your answers.</li>\r\n<li>The strict university examination procedures must be followed.</li>\r\n<li>The Board of Examiners  reserves the right to disqualify all scores from  candidates if it determines that the required academic integrity procedures were not followed.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #ff6600;\">At the end of the examination</span></p>\r\n<p>When you have completed the examination, you must submit your answers from the summary page.</p>\r\n<p>Click on the  <span style=\"color: #ffffff;\"> <span style=\"background-color: #ff7f50; padding: 5px; border-radius: 4px;\">Finish attempt</span>\"</span>link under the question number panel on the left hand side.</p>\r\n<p>At the bottom of the next page. Click the button <span style=\"background-color: #ff7f50; padding: 5px; border-radius: 4px; color: #ffffff;\">Submit all and finish</span> and then confirm that you wish to submit.</p>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #ff6600;\">For this examination your score will not be provided.</span></h3>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<h1>PLEASE PROCEED ONCE EXAMINATION IS OPEN</h1>",
